{"tid":2067701,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"可能是「最後」了？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-17T07:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T07:37:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec430a0d514e05668a44feadf9b649d58c179b57","tid":2067701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200617/20938547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938547%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=7bf28398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200617%2F20938547%2F&h=d6b5317d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200617/20938547/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n可能是「最後」了？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200617/large/1592296113_64c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200617%2Flarge%2F1592296113_64c8.jpg&h=30146fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武肺肆虐，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，時間甚為緊迫。<br />\n<br />\n籌備新書需時，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，所以此決策有點離地。<br />\n<br />\n希望多些來客？抑或量體溫戴口罩大家有距離的「限制入場」呢？如何消毒？人多了黑警「執法」嗎？──看來什麼「限聚令」，只針對示威者，雙重標準，司馬昭之心。往年每有逾百萬人入場，當局亦為了入場費吧？看到報導，出版社也特地提醒死線，所以還得趕工。<br />\n<br />\n以前我們並不很重視書展，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。明日陰晴未定，不管了。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"28dab9f6211561c7ee8ca20e6a233b3f3ca93925","tid":2067701,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"